Time for the top nine! I’ve had a rollercoaster year I don’t know where to begin but the main thing I am insanely grateful for is all of my amazing, wonderful customers. You are the reason I have some how managed to open my own studio, the reason I live, the reason I am happy and the reason I get out of bed every day. Love you all and can’t wait to spend more time with you all in 2020 xox
